      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it's just... the idea of \"rest\" sounds so good, but i don't think i can ever actually rest while i'm still here. even when i sleep, the noise and the guilt of failing just follow me. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace, to stop the noise and just finally be still, is something much more permanent than just taking a nap.",
